snippet.title: CODE VEIN Character Trailer: Yakumo Shionome | X1, PS4, Steam
snippet.description:
"“I’m Yakumo Shionome, I’ll be looking forward to seeing you in action”  

Armed with his Hounds Blood Veil, Yakumo will thrash anyone who gets in his way! Prepare to rise, #CODEVEIN launches September 28th on Xbox One, PS4, and Steam! Pre-order today! https://bandainam.co/codevein
